    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Sinezona platyspira new species. West Norfolk Ridge, W of Cape Reinga, 34.298 ˚ S, 168.430 ˚ E, 785 – 800 m A. Holotype. (NMNZ M. 301400). B. Paratype (NMNZ M. 301399). Scale bars shell = 0.5 mm. Scale bars protoconch = 100 µm." ;
